Background
 This directory is used to house all build related scripting and configuration files for rpm, deb, etc

Directories
 deb       - Debian related build tree (Supported)
 rpm       - Fedora/RHEL related build tre (Supported)
 tar       - Tar related installation items (Experimental
 distutils - Python distutils related build tree (Experimental)

Test:
 Ubuntu 9.04: rpm & deb
 Fedora 11: rpm only
